00:29:24,366 --> 00:29:25,366
Huh?

497
00:29:25,700 --> 00:29:27,300
Isn't this Ms. Oh's?

498
00:29:37,233 --> 00:29:41,153
Jung-rok hasn't been eating well
ever since he accepted the case,

499
00:29:41,233 --> 00:29:43,466
and I'm worried he may
collapse at this rate.

