503
00:29:53,600 --> 00:29:55,886
I'm just a bit tired.

504
00:29:55,966 --> 00:29:57,620
It is hard, isn't it?

505
00:29:57,700 --> 00:30:00,586
But you'll be done for the day
with this next scene,

506
00:30:00,666 --> 00:30:02,500
so let's hurry up and go home.

507
00:30:03,300 --> 00:30:04,366
Alright.

508
00:30:09,600 --> 00:30:10,753
Huh?

509
00:30:10,833 --> 00:30:12,333
This is the office number.

510
00:30:13,900 --> 00:30:15,933
Hello? This is Oh Yoon-seo.

511
00:30:17,633 --> 00:30:19,166
Ah, Pil-ki.

512
00:30:20,666 --> 00:30:21,986
Did you need to
talk to me about something?

513
00:30:22,066 --> 00:30:24,386
Well, the thing is…
I'll be supporting Mr. Kwon

514
00:30:24,466 --> 00:30:28,386
